{"tid":2448790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國駐港澳總領事館批評有親中傳媒散播疫情假消息","createTime":"2021-03-16T07:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T07:32:43.000Z","uid":156254,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7a0a253a0dd89150f3d27cff0eb22763da208092","tid":2448790,"uid":156254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T07:30:07.000Z","msg":"美國駐港澳總領事館否認有報道指，兩名感染新型冠狀病毒的職員曾拒絕隔離，強調完全配合特區政府安排。 《大公報》和《文匯報》引述消息人士指，兩人以外交豁免權為由拒絕接受隔離安排。領事館在社交網站發文，不點名指有中國操控的傳媒散播假消息，強調有關報道並不真確，反對在重大的公共衛生議題上散播假消息。帖文又引用特區政府昨晚的新聞稿，指領事館一直全力配合政府各項防疫工作。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383198\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2383198&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=be3a6007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383198</a>"},{"pid":"aa72564d8f0c8092168f82b9e9e7581983081565","tid":2448790,"uid":76710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T07:30:51.000Z","msg":"大公文匯垃撚圾"},{"pid":"58011fb3a6ec560c0f3463d00ef4e6ef9f14bdba","tid":2448790,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa72564d8f0c8092168f82b9e9e7581983081565","tid":2448790,"uid":76710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T07:30:51.000Z","msg":"大公文匯垃撚圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T07:32:43.000Z","msg":"黨報"}]}